Type: Package
Package: SummaryTables
Title: Publication-Ready Summary Tables for Jamovi
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Nour Edin", "Darwish", , "nouredindarwish@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-5527-4539"))
Description: A comprehensive module for creating publication-ready summary
    tables in jamovi, powered by gtsummary. Includes four key analyses.
    'Summary Table' creates classic "Table 1" summaries, including group
    comparisons with automatic statistical testing, effect sizes, and
    p-value adjustments. 'Continuous Table' summarizes a single continuous
    outcome stratified across multiple categorical variables, including
    automatic statistical testing and p-value adjustments. 'Cross Table'
    summarizes the association between two categorical variables using
    cross-tabulations, including automatic statistical testing. 'Likert
    Table' summarizes Likert scale items.  Features include direct export
    to Word (.docx), 16 languages, and pre-built formatting for major
    journals.
